title: reinstalling league still appliying patches
body: at 5500 patches now 84% ive uninstalled reinstalled run as admin, nothing is working what do i do??

replies.body:
Panic.

Then, go over to [this page](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/202969434-Patching-Issues) and see if you've tried all that before. What problem are you persistently facing?
